 wiring for GLM-5.2 to MiMo-v2.5-Pro fallback\",\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"priority\": \"high\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"content\": \"phase_synthesis: Compile research.md with findings, eliminated alternatives, open questions\",\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"priority\": \"high\"\n  }\n]","metadata":{"todos":[{"content":"phase_init: Create config, strategy, state log, findings registry in lineages/glm52-1","status":"in_progress","priority":"high"},{"content":"Iteration 1: Structural layout — validate the deep-loop-runtime into deep-loop-workflows merge shape","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Iteration 2: Bidirectional path-coupling repair","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Iteration 3: system-spec-kit tooling-borrow","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Iteration 4: Reference migration across commands/agents/READMEs/advisor-corpus","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Iteration 5: fallback-router.ts wiring for GLM-5.2 to MiMo-v2.5-Pro fallback","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"phase_synthesis: Compile research.md with findings, eliminated alternatives, open questions","status":"pending","priority":"high"}],"truncated":false},"title":"7 todos","time":{"start":1783488105710,"end":1783488105712}},"id":"prt_f402ccce7001GmB4VTHCD5xdD7","sessionID":"ses_0bfd48e01ffew5W9Qhj3V2EB2W","messageID":"msg_f402c820d001Q2SrdroCnosJxP"}}
{"type":"text","timestamp":1783488105731,"sessionID":"ses_0bfd48e01ffew5W9Qhj3V2EB2W","part":{"id":"prt_f402ccce2001rmgUfEZhkGKv0S","messageID":"msg_f402c820d001Q2SrdroCnosJxP","sessionID":"ses_0bfd48e01ffew5W9Qhj3V2EB2W","type":"text","text":"This is one of 20 fan-out replicas — specifically the `glm52-1` GLM-5.2 lineage. I'm both orchestrator and executor (I am glm-5.2). Let me set up the todo list and examine the lineages dir, plan, and key code structures.","time":{"start":1783488105698,"end":1783488105727}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783488105731,"sessionID":"ses_0bfd48e01ffew5W9Qhj3V2EB2W","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_4922fb0ff3394e18a8538cf7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages"},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages</path>\n<type>directory</type>\n<entries>\nglm52-1/\nglm52-2/\ngpt55-fast-1/\ngpt55-fast-10/\ngpt55-fast-2/\ngpt55-fast-3/\ngpt55-fast-4/\ngpt55-fast-5/\ngpt55-fast-6/\ngpt55-fast-7/\ngpt55-fast-8/\ngpt55-fast-9/\n\n(12 entries)\n</entries>","metadata":{"preview":"glm52-1/\nglm52-2/\ngpt55-fast-1/\ngpt55-fast-10/\ngpt55-fast-2/\ngpt55-fast-3/\ngpt55-fast-4/\ngpt55-fast-5/\ngpt55-fast-6/\ngpt55-fast-7/\ngpt55-fast-8/\ngpt55-fast-9/","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"directory","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages","entries":["glm52-1/","glm52-2/","gpt55-fast-1/","gpt55-fast-10/","gpt55-fast-2/","gpt55-fast-3/","gpt55-fast-4/","gpt55-fast-5/","gpt55-fast-6/","gpt55-fast-7/","gpt55-fast-8/","gpt55-fast-9/"],"offset":1,"totalEntries":12,"truncated":false}},"title":".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages","time":{"start":1783488105712,"end":1783488105728}},"id":"prt_f402cccef001WpytkbAgtkxzLC","sessionID":"ses_0bfd48e01ffew5W9Qhj3V2EB2W","messageID":"msg_f402c820d001Q2SrdroCnosJxP"}}
