equires) as primary merge risk\", \"reason\": \"Loud MODULE_NOT_FOUND; 50 silent string literals are real exposure\", \"evidence\": \"compile-command-contracts.cjs:15-288\", \"iterations\": [2]},\n    {\"approach\": \"Inline review-research-paths.cjs into system-deep-loop during merge\", \"reason\": \"Intentional single-source seam; duplicating reintroduces drift\", \"evidence\": \"artifact-root.cjs:5-9\", \"iterations\": [3]},\n    {\"approach\": \"Migration uniform across all surfaces\", \"reason\": \"Tiered: 2 automated guards + ungated prose\", \"evidence\": \"mode-registry.json:16; aliases.ts:109\", \"iterations\": [4]},\n    {\"approach\": \"Wire fallback-router during the merge\", \"reason\": \"Out of scope + moving-target + approval-guard rejects unapproved swaps\", \"evidence\": \"spec.md:69-75; fallback-router.ts:411-420\", \"iterations\": [5]}\n  ]\n}\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/glm52-1/deep-research-findings-registry.json"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/glm52-1/deep-research-findings-registry.json","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/glm52-1/deep-research-findings-registry.json","time":{"start":1783488884317,"end":1783488884321}},"id":"prt_f4038ae5c001wGW7WYmkXWjPG9","sessionID":"ses_0bfd48e01ffew5W9Qhj3V2EB2W","messageID":"msg_f403847e60014nXn3EK1RzFM6B"}}
