{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783488978554,"sessionID":"ses_0bfd48e01ffew5W9Qhj3V2EB2W","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_ee34f97aa4da4e4e9d70526f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Deep Research Dashboard — glm52-1\n\n> Auto-generated from JSONL, strategy, and findings registry.\n\n## Iteration Table\n\n| run | focus | newInfoRatio | findings | status |\n|-----|-------|--------------|----------|--------|\n| 1 | Structural layout: directories, fold targets, mechanical safety | 1.0 | 5 | complete |\n| 2 | Bidirectional coupling: requires + string literals, silent vs loud | 0.85 | 4 | complete |\n| 3 | system-spec-kit tooling-borrow residual: depth-invariance, net verdict | 0.55 | 4 | complete |\n| 4 | Reference migration surface: 6 tiers by loudness, advisor coupled-pair | 0.6 | 5 | complete |\n| 5 | fallback-router.ts wiring: zero callers, 4-piece cost, verdict | 0.45 | 5 | complete |\n\n## Question Status\n\n5/5 answered\n\n- Q1 Structural layout — ANSWERED (iter 1)\n- Q2 Bidirectional coupling repair — ANSWERED (iter 2)\n- Q3 system-spec-kit tooling-borrow — ANSWERED (iter 3)\n- Q4 Reference migration surface — ANSWERED (iter 4)\n- Q5 fallback-router.ts wiring — ANSWERED (iter 5)\n\n## Convergence Trend\n\nLast 3 ratios: 0.55 → 0.6 → 0.45 (descending)\n\n## Dead Ends\n\n- Resolve 8 node_modules reach-ins: already resolved (bare specifiers)\n- Direction A as primary risk: loud requires; silent literals are real exposure\n- Inline review-research-paths.cjs: intentional single-source seam\n- Uniform migration surface: tiered (2 guards + ungated prose)\n- Wire fallback-router during merge: out of scope + approval-guard blocks\n\n## Blocked Stops\n\nNone — legal-stop gates passed on first STOP candidate (all questions answered + maxIterations).\n\n## Next Focus\n\nCONVERGED — synthesis complete.\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unificatio